name: ENG105
description:
[W] and [A] are left and right. 

[Space] is jump 

Dash is [B] 

Double jump is [Space] but in the air 

 

Dash and jump need to be unlocked. 

Signs are a work in progress.  

Door on the left goes to tutorial, door on right goes to level. 

You’ll have 30 seconds to get as high as possible.
